{"tid":1142320,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"DC9載客不忘打機　乘客勸阻反被怒睥？","createTime":"2019-05-07T04:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T05:36:14.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74df14f38dee7f4a514691899afd404a74b06016","tid":1142320,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"的哥載客不忘打機 乘客勸阻反被怒睥？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y4JUYi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y4JUYi&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c19daefa\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y4JUYi</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/photo/bkn-20190507114335538-0507_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190507115837\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190507%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190507114335538-0507_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190507115837&h=aec76813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇嚟司機係打機高手喎。<br />\n<br />\n的士乘客周一（6日）上載影片至其社交網站，只見當時的士正於隧道內行駛，惟司機的手機固定在軚盤上方，屏幕中的遊戲畫面不停跳動，司機更抽空不時點擊遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n該乘客批評司機駕駛時打機非常危險：「我叫佢揸車可唔可以唔打機，好危險，佢睥咗我一吓，冇再撳，但也都冇熄個屏幕一路望住」。"},{"pid":"501d287be89271b540bbd1245ae1312d1d49f66a","tid":1142320,"uid":25148,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"司機就司機啦 的佢老母哥咩報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb1b414a352c042816f195a90cc2f91fba44339","tid":1142320,"uid":2521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"玩Taxi Crush<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}